another time and somehow

00:17:01.370 --> 00:17:06.750 align:middle line:84%
designing a new way of fueling
our body and our brain,

00:17:06.750 --> 00:17:12.140 align:middle line:84%
which is still needs
energy, but in, I would say,

00:17:12.140 --> 00:17:17.240 align:middle line:84%
a more reasonable way
considering the way of life

00:17:17.240 --> 00:17:18.770 align:middle line:90%
modern humans have today.

