>> The way we're living at
the moment is clearly not

00:17:26.930 --> 00:17:30.000 align:middle line:84%
compatible with our
evolutionary heritage.

00:17:30.000 --> 00:17:32.000 align:middle line:84%
Many of us are
too fat and suffer

00:17:32.000 --> 00:17:34.730 align:middle line:84%
