at the reason why

00:34:53.340 --> 00:34:55.830 align:middle line:84%
people are changing their
lives and their behavior,

00:34:55.830 --> 00:34:58.800 align:middle line:84%
then the first priority is their
health and their well-being,

00:34:58.800 --> 00:35:03.660 align:middle line:84%
