leaving a footprint,

00:35:06.190 --> 00:35:07.712 align:middle line:90%
and you can't wipe it away.

00:35:07.712 --> 00:35:09.420 align:middle line:84%
There's more and more
people in the world

00:35:09.420 --> 00:35:11.370 align:middle line:90%
and not enough resources.

00:35:11.370 --> 00:35:14.430 align:middle line:84%
And the focus on feeding animals
means some people go hungry.

00:35:14.430 --> 00:35:19.920 align:middle line:90%


00:35:19.920 --> 00:35:23.730 align:middle line:84%
Once we number 10 billion
people in 20, 30, 40 years,

00:35:23.730 --> 00:35:25.680 align:middle line:84%
the planet will be
too small for us,

00:35:25.680 --> 00:35:27.880 align:middle line:84%
and we will have to
consume directly,

00:35:27.880 --> 00:35:30.450 align:middle line:84%
meaning we have to
