It's just not there.

00:35:38.550 --> 00:35:47.730 align:middle line:90%


00:35:47.730 --> 00:35:50.010 align:middle line:84%
For Anna-Lena
Klapp and her boss,

00:35:50.010 --> 00:35:54.420 align:middle line:84%
Sebastian Joy from the German
Vegetarian Union, the animal

00:35:54.420 --> 00:35:58.530 align:middle line:84%
sanctuary and freed animals
are worthy of his story

00:35:58.530 --> 00:36:01.400 align:middle line:90%
for this circular.

00:36:01.400 --> 00:36:06.480 align:middle line:84%
Here, pictures can portray
what bland numbers often can't.

00:36:06.480 --> 00:36:11.562 align:middle line:84%
One tangible example says
more than any statistics.

00:36:11.562 --> 00:36:12.520 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:36:12.520 --> 00:36:15.860 align:middle line:84%
