make a connection to it,

00:36:36.170 --> 00:36:37.790 align:middle line:84%
and realize that
it's a sentiment

00:36:37.790 --> 00:36:39.770 align:middle line:84%
being that just wants
to live and be happy.

00:36:39.770 --> 00:36:45.570 align:middle line:90%


00:36:45.570 --> 00:36:50.940 align:middle line:84%
The story is too
good not to be used.

00:36:50.940 --> 00:36:54.200 align:middle line:90%
>> [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]

00:36:54.200 --> 00:36:57.920 align:middle line:84%
>> We try not to point fingers,
